<?oxygen NVDLSchema="../schema/epidoc.nvdl"?>

<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="supp-publication" xml:lang="en">
    <head>Publication information</head>
    <p>Information about the current publication and licensing status of the inscription/papyrus
        edition should be recorded in the <gi>titleStmt</gi> and <gi>publicationStmt</gi> elements
        in the header.</p>
    <p>
        <specList>
            <specDesc key="titleStmt"/>
            <specDesc key="title"/>
            <specDesc key="editor"/>
            <specDesc key="publicationStmt"/>
            <specDesc key="idno"/>
            <specDesc key="availability"/>
            <specDesc key="licence"/>
        </specList>
    </p>

    <egXML xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/Examples">
        <titleStmt>
            <title>Verse honours for Oikoumenios</title>
            <editor>Joyce M. Reynolds</editor>
            <editor>Charlotte M. Roueché</editor>
        </titleStmt>
    </egXML>

    <egXML xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/Examples">
        <publicationStmt>
            <authority>IOSPE Project</authority>
            <idno type="filename">Byz212</idno>
            <availability>
                <licence target="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/"> Licensed under a
                    Creative Commons-Attribution 3.0 licence. </licence>
            </availability>
        </publicationStmt>
    </egXML>

    <p>Additional information can be added to state particular licencing status of photos for
        example.</p>
    <egXML xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/Examples"
        corresp="http://edh-www.adw.uni-heidelberg.de/edh/inschrift/HD058118">
        <graphic n="UTS_5" url="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:UTS_5.png">
            <desc> Frgament from Ulpia Traiana Sarmizegetusa. Face and Drawing. <ref type="license"
                    target="creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/"> Licensed under the Creative
                    Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 Unported license. </ref>
            </desc>
        </graphic>
    </egXML>

    <p>Also more specific licencing status associated with the translation might be expressed in the
        same way if needed.</p>

    <egXML xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/Examples">
        <div type="translation">
            <p> To the emperor Caesar Nerva Traianus, son of the divine Nerva, Augustus, Germanicus,
                Dacicus </p>
            <desc>
                <ref type="license" target="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/">
                    Licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 Unported licence.
                </ref>
            </desc>
        </div>
    </egXML>
    
    <divGen type="seealso"/>

    <div xml:id="supp-publication-responsibility">
        <head>Responsibility for this section</head>
        <listBibl>
            <bibl><respStmt><resp>author</resp><name>Gabriel Bodard</name></respStmt></bibl>
            <bibl><respStmt><resp>author</resp><name>Pietro Liuzzo</name></respStmt></bibl>
        </listBibl>
    </div>
</div>
